label: year
comment: Year corresponding to this observation and is described in YYYY format, for eg. 2020.

label: evaluationYear
comment: The period during which a survey or assessment has been carried out.

label: loanType
comment: The specific type of financial assistance provided to individuals or entities. For eg., crop loan, term loan etc.

label: loanTargetAmount
comment: The total amount of money planned to be disbursed as agricultural credit for a particular loan type, by the government or financial institution within a certain time period.

label: loanAchievementAmount
comment: The total amount of money actually disbursed as agricultural credit for a particular loan type, by the government or financial institution within a certain time period.

label: achievementRate
comment: The ratio of the actual loan amount disbursed to the loan amount targeted to be disbursed for a particular loan type, expressed as a percentage, denoting the level of attainment of the credit goals. It is calculated as (loanAchievementAmount / loanTargetAmount)*100.

label: totalTargetAmount
comment: The total amount of money targeted to be disbursed across all loan types within a specific period.

label: totalAchievementAmount
comment: The total amount of money actually disbursed across all loan types within a specific period.

label: totalAchievementRate
comment: The ratio of the actual loan amount disbursed in total to the total loan amount targeted to be disbursed across all loan types, expressed as a percentage, denoting the level of attainment of the credit goals.
